 Genesis - Stargate returns to Channel Seven

Ahhhh... here I am at very long last!

Greetings Gaters, I am Raziel - First Born Lieutenant to Lord Kain.
This first scripture of mine details the return of our beloved Circle of Woes to the dark twisted broadcasting of Se7en.

As some of you may already know, the frozen wastes of Salt Lake City will dominate the greater part of Se7en over the next few weeks. I am assured that the next immediate airing date following these icy games will see the rebirth of sierra gulf I, beginning with the deceptive episode "The Vth Man".

This information applies solely to harbour dwelling Sydneysiders with the possibility of return to sunshine swimming Brisbane and the vile Melbourne soon after.

The sun sets even now and I must journey into the depths of the night. Thank You.
